Subject: [PATCH 1777/4530] drm/amdgpu: add cache flush workaround to gfx8
 emit_fence

The same workaround is used for gfx7.
Both PAL and Mesa use it for gfx8 too, so port this commit to
gfx_v8_0_ring_emit_fence_gfx.

